description:
Sweet Sinema pays homage to a classic tale of aging &quot;first wives&quot; and callous, cheating husbands. Former college friends Raylene, Nina and Helly reconnect at now-famous movie star Helly's book-signing. As they reminisce over lunch, the three ladies discover they've all been dumped by cheating husbands in favor of young, hot bimbos. While passive &quot;doormat&quot; Nina keeps her faith that husband Jay will return, Raylene and Helly decide to even the score with cheating exes Mark and Evan. A fun, sexy tale that explores the powerful fantasy of older/younger sex.

